'''Jeff Stanzler''' is an American [[screenwriter]] and [[film director|director]].  He wrote and directed the 2005 [[psychological thriller]], [[Sorry, Haters]], an "official selection" in both the [[Toronto Film Festival|Toronto]] and [[American Film Institute]] [[film festival]]s.  He is currently working on a [[Documentary film|documentary]] about [[politics]] in [[West Africa]].  He's married to Annouchka Yameogo-Stanzler.

==Selected filmography==
*''[[Sorry, Haters]]'' (2005)

